Beautiful 2-story home nestled in the back of the neighborhood. Greeted by hardwood flooring and 2 story foyer, Separate dining room, office, ?open kitchen with eat-in breakfast area, all-electric home, Kitchen overlooking family room w/ fireplace. Upstairs you will find the spacious owner's suite, tray ceilings, large bathroom with double vanity, sep tub and shower. 2 secondary bedrroms and full bath. ?Relax in your sunroom or step outside to the backyard retreat, complete with storage shed and ample space for outdoor activities. Minutes away from Tanger Outlets, restaurants, and Exit 149 on I-85. ?Dining, and a short distance to shopping and dining in Historic Downtown Commerce.
